Description: Part of the rim and shoulder of a tall jar: of brown pottery, with the remains of an incised inscription on the exterior. Good condition.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: W. M. F. Petrie, 'Abydos' I (London, 1902), pl.XLV, 46; A. Roveri and F. Tiradritte [eds.], 'Kemet: Alle Sorgenti del Tempo' (Ravenna, 1998), p.230 [191].
Exhibition history: 2015, 19th June - 5th Sept. Wrexham County Borough Museum.
